---
title: Crumbled Crispy Falafel Salad with Garlicky Hummus Drizzle
description: Here's a new, tasty way to enjoy falafel! This salad is a breeze to whip up and full of texture from those crispy falafel crumbles. The garlicky hummus drizzled over top adds a nice 'creamy' quality without any dairy!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/crumbled-crispy-falafel-salad-7ed8de98.jpg
